<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Where is this fine shield found? What MoB? Lvl? and zone? Thanks for any info you can post.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Wrathius</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-21 11:56:31</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is a quest shield.. <BR>
<BR>
Need the icon and ingot of Nebbletob the Devout. <BR>
<BR>
Devout Icon is on a Minotour Sentry in the mino mines in <BR>
Steamfont (lvl 35 or so). <BR>
<BR>
Devout Ingot is on some great white beast in a hidden cave under the ice river in Everfrost (lvl unknown).<BR>
<BR>
You also need 3 enchanted bars of Platinum.<BR>
<BR>
You give these to Gavel in the Temple of Solusek Ro to receive the shield.<BR>
<BR>
I currently hold the Devout Icon on Bertox.. so if you want me to help.. gimme a tell! =) <BR>
<BR>
Wrathius<BR>
Enchanter<BR>
Bertoxxulos<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
