<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Shayeras</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-02 12:06:20</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The great beast is the Glacier bear in the Underground caverns in Everfrost. He is about level 30 and a tough kill, from what I have read. I am seeking someone to hunt this beast for the pelt he drops as well. If anyone on Povar is looking for the Cleric item the bear drops, perhaps we can team of and drop this foul beast together.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
