<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>If you're serious about camping the glacier bear, go to www.eqshaman.com, to quests, and read about getting the Totemic Helm. The shammies need a Glacier Bear Pelt(from the Glacier Bear) for the helm and there's great guides on how to find the stupid thing.</font></td></tr></table>
