<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lonark Stormhammer</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-12 05:53:31</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am a shaman and i have killed the glacier bear 6 times, yes 6 times! I dont camp the bear hardcore, i play late at night when not very many people are on, so what I do is every time im in the everfrost area, I take a run down into the cave and do a quick "sense animals" spell. if i see a glacier bear i go kill, if not, i dont care, i come back later. Anyway, outta those 6 times he dropped the ingot twice and sad to say i had to let the seconf ingot rot with the bear since I already had the one from before. Anyway, I wanted to try to help a cleric finish the quest. If any cleric from Luclin needs the ingot, look me up. I'd be happy to help ya out.<BR>
<BR>
Lonark Stormhammer 31st shaman of Luclin</font></td></tr></table>
